{"tid":2161414,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Heat Project回歸？香港團隊Steam免費上架　90後玩家9個經典回憶","createTime":"2020-08-17T14:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T09:38:58.000Z","uid":48161,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"29574e40907be3419ff971db8d1feab832c7acdb","tid":2161414,"uid":48161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"01唔貼link<br />\n<br />\n【Heat Project】80﹑90後最大的打機回憶，可能是盛極一時的 online game 狂熱時期，走入網吧都能見到《巨商》﹑《童話》﹑《彩虹冒險》等線上遊戲，而 fps 類型中不得不提的一定是《Heat Project》。近日在 Steam 上發現，有一個香港團隊把《Heat Project》重製，將會放上 Steam 讓玩家免費遊玩，用上 Source 引擎提升畫面外，更把大量回憶重新帶回來。<br />\n<br />\n《HEAT REBORN》<br />\n<br />\n由香港團隊打造的《Heat Project》重製版《HEAT REBORN》，改用 Source 引擎令遊戲畫面提升回現今較易接受的水平，不過由於是新引擎，舊有的 Bug 就不能再用，同時有防外掛系統，玩家不用擔心穿牆自動瞄頭。如果十多年前，你也有在《Heat Project》中耗過多個通宵和暑假，那這隻在 Steam 上架的免費遊戲，絕對不能錯過。<br />\n<br />\n=========================================================<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1219590/HEAT_REBORN/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1219590%2FHEAT_REBORN%2F&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21PGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=48cffccd\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/1219590/HEAT_REBORN/</a><br />\nSteam真係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望年尾真係出到啦<br />\n到時有性趣入部windows laptop玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家用MBP Parallels Win 10始終唔太好"},{"pid":"dc2a0fe373675700fe0724825b62023c0fe680d7","tid":2161414,"uid":48161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abae158a707548e9dead36f5e38246b298cc4d58","tid":2161414,"uid":114074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:05:51.000Z","msg":"旺角個場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53635fbc004fc1032c1214e45993d1aa6521b5b6","tid":2161414,"uid":48161,"like":0